udicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHM/110%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c395%2c20210524%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCHM,110,上訴,395,20210524,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"395","JDATE":"20210524","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}